original_text: [CLS] kris tiffany maslog janson ( born december 21, 1989 ) simply known as kris janson, is a filipino beauty pageant titleholder from cebu city, crowned binibining pilipinas intercontinental 2014 at the binibining pilipinas 2014 pageant held on march 30th, 2014 at the smart araneta coliseum, quezon city, philippines.
